channel.description:
EuromaidanPR is a self-funded, alternative news media outlet born on the barricades of #Maidan and now aim to be the #1 Independent Citizen Media about #Ukraine, investigating, giving analysis and reporting the Truth.

Our reporters are normal people and our writers all volunteers.

EMPR is entirely independent, reliant on our volunteers and we reject any owner or large donor who may affect our independence.
